snippet.title: 【MV】Natasha "X. THE FLOWER" (Special English Ver.) 【MementoMori】
snippet.description:
This is a Lament (original character theme song) from MementoMori, a new RPG that released on 10.18.2022.

==================================
A grieving girl who ravished her country,
for it ripped her parents away from her.
“Natasha”
==================================

影片提供英、韓、繁中、簡中字幕。
视频提供英语、韩语、繁体中文、简体中文字幕。
이 동영상은 한국어, 영어, 중국어(번자체, 간자체) 자막을 지원합니다.
